snippet.title: My Supermarket Early Access Release
snippet.description:
Exciting news!
We're officially launching out the Steam Early Access!

Welcome to the grand opening of "My Supermarket" - an exciting new game where you get to fulfill your dream of managing and customizing your very own supermarket.

In this Early Access release, we invite you to step in aboard this new adventure, have fun and also help develop the future of the game! ❤️


Check out more details on MY SUPERMARKET on the Steam Page, Itch.io and official discord server! 😍

STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1244910/My_SuperMarket/
Discord: https://discord.gg/JZsQrn9HJK

Made by Nero Games
https://nerogames.pt/
support@nerogames.pt
